Privacy Policy for ليطمئن قلبي.

Last Updated: [Update Date]

Please read this privacy policy carefully before using the ليطمئن قلبي application. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information. By using the ليطمئن قلبي application, you agree to this policy.

Information We Collect:

We collect the information you provide when using the ليطمئن قلبي application. This information may include:

Location: We request access to your location to determine the direction of Qibla and prayer times.
Personal Data: We collect personal information, such as your name (if provided), to personalize your experience.
Usage: We gather information about how you use the ليطمئن قلبي application to improve performance and the user experience.
Use of Information:

We use the information we collect for various purposes, including:

Improving Our App: We use the information to understand how you use and enhance our application.
Customizing Your Experience: We use the information to personalize your experience within our app.
Qibla Direction and Prayer Times: We collect your location to provide accurate information about Qibla direction and prayer times.
Contacting You: We may use your contact information to respond to your inquiries and feedback.
Sharing Information:

We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties outside the ليطمئن قلبي application without your consent, except when required by law.

Protecting Information:

We take reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, please be aware that the internet is not a completely secure environment, and the security of information cannot be guaranteed.

